{"title":"Migration of Hexo+Github Pages","date":"2020-03-10T07:30:11.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 10, 2020","L":"03/10/2020","MM-DD":"03-10"},"link":"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages","tags":["website"],"updated":"2020-03-14T17:34:33.312Z","content":"<p>Due to the novel coronavirus epidemic situation, I can’t go back to the laboratory  to update my website. Fortunately, I backed up the website data. I want to update the website through my pc.</p>\n<p>Here are my implementation steps. (I will not repeat section 1 and 2, <a href=\"https://thswind.github.io/2020/01/14/hexo%2Bgithub%20pages%20deploy\">https://thswind.github.io/2020/01/14/hexo%2Bgithub%20pages%20deploy</a>)</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-Install-node-js\">1 Install node.js<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#1-Install-node-js\"></a></h2><h2 id=\"2-Install-Git\">2 Install Git<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#2-Install-Git\"></a></h2><h2 id=\"3-Install-hexo\">3 Install hexo<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#3-Install-hexo\"></a></h2><blockquote>\n<p>Open cmd console, switch to :</p>\n<p>​    F:\\mywebsite\\blog</p>\n<p>And input this command, as below:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog&gt;npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>initial your blog:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog&gt;hexo init thswind</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Warning: If your are failed, probably because of your internet speed is not good.</p>\n<p>Switch to thswind, and install some dependencies：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog\\thswind&gt;npm install</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Install a deployer:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog\\thswind&gt;npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-Migration\">4 Migration<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#4-Migration\"></a></h2><blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>copy package.json package-lock.json from old pc to new pc</li>\n<li>copy thswind/source from old pc to thswind/source to new pc</li>\n<li>copy scaffolds to new pc</li>\n<li>copy themes to new pc</li>\n<li>copy blog\\thswind\\_config.yml to new pc</li>\n<li>copy thswind\\node_modules to new pc</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Problems\">Problems<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#Problems\"></a></h2><blockquote>\n<p>After you finished  these steps, some error may occur because of China’s complex internet environment. How to deal with it? just follow me.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>ERROR Plugin load failed: hexo-renderer-scss</p>\n<p>To solve this problem, you can through this command:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt;    F:\\mywebsite\\blog\\thswind&gt;npm install hexo-renderer-scss --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>   If failed again, it means you can’t visit <a href=\"http://www.github.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.github.com</a> normally. You can visit it indirectly through ‘mirror’ website. <a href=\"http://www.gitee.com/mirrors\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.gitee.com/mirrors</a> is a good choice.</p>\n   <figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt;    F:\\mywebsite\\blog\\thswind&gt;npm install -g mirror-config-china --registry=http://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;   F:\\mywebsite\\blog\\thswind&gt;npm install node-sass</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Reference\"><a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#Reference\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Reference:\"></a><em>Reference:</em></h3><p>   <a href=\"https://www.fangr.cc/2017/09/27/hexo-workflow.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.fangr.cc/2017/09/27/hexo-workflow.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Notes\">Notes:<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#Notes\"></a></h2><blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>Maybe because of different os, there will be many warning and error information in cmd console. If you haven’t found a failed, then you can ignore it, or deal with it according to the tips.</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n","next":{"title":"math_formula_test","link":"2020/01/16/math-formula-test"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages/","toc":[{"title":"1 Install node.js","id":"1-Install-node-js","index":"1"},{"title":"2 Install Git","id":"2-Install-Git","index":"2"},{"title":"3 Install hexo","id":"3-Install-hexo","index":"3"},{"title":"4 Migration","id":"4-Migration","index":"4"},{"title":"Problems","id":"Problems","index":"5","children":[{"title":"","id":"Reference","index":"5.1"}]},{"title":"Notes:","id":"Notes","index":"6"}],"reward":true}